This documentation provides an overview of how to plan a <%= vars.ops_manager_first %> installation.


## <a id='overview'></a> Overview

In planning an <%= vars.ops_manager %> installation, you should:

- Review the Requirements for your IaaS.

- Refer to the Reference Architecture for your IaaS.

- Assess your platform needs, including capacity, availability, container support, host OS, resource isolation, and geographical distribution. Discuss with your <%= vars.company_name %> contact.

For all of the above, the specifics depend on the IaaS that you are deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> to. The contents of this documentation are organized by IaaS.


